t-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 18px\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"HEIGHT: auto; WHITE-SPACE: normal; WORD-SPACING: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-ALIGN: left; PADDING-TOP: 0px; FONT: 12px/21px 宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; ORPHANS: 2; WIDOWS: 2; LETTER-SPACING: normal; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span id=\"ContentBody\" style=\"HEIGHT: auto; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\"><strong style=\"HEIGHT: auto; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 18px; HEIGHT: auto; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\">一、培养目标</span></strong></span></p><p style=\"HEIGHT: auto; WHITE-SPACE: normal; WORD-SPACING: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-ALIGN: left; PADDING-TOP: 0px; FONT: 12px/21px 宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; ORPHANS: 2; WIDOWS: 2; LETTER-SPACING: normal; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span id=\"ContentBody\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 18px; HEIGHT: auto; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\">培养适应我国社会主义现代化需要的，具有创新能力、实践能力和创业精神，在德、智、体全面发展，在专业方面具有合理的知识结构，较强的研究能力以及管理实践能力的高层次管理人才。具体要求是：</span></p><p style=\"HEIGHT: auto; WHITE-SPACE: normal; WORD-SPACING: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-ALIGN: left; PADDING-TOP: 0px; FONT: 12px/21px 宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; ORPHANS: 2; WIDOWS: 2; LETTER-SPACING: normal; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span id=\"ContentBody\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 18px; HEIGHT: auto; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\">1</span><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 18px\">．掌握马列主义，毛泽东思想和邓小平理论的基本原理，具有正确的世界观，人生观和价值观，热爱祖国，拥护中国共产党的领导，遵纪守法，具有良好的道德品质和科研作风，有献身于科学的事业心，具有高度的责任感和合作精神，积极为社会主义现代化建设事业服务。</span></p><p style=\"HEIGHT: auto; WHITE-SPACE: normal; WORD-SPACING: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-ALIGN: left; PADDING-TOP: 0px; FONT: 12px/21px 宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; ORPHANS: 2; WIDOWS: 2; LETTER-SPACING: normal; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span id=\"ContentBody\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 18px; HEIGHT: auto; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\">2</span><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 18px\">．\r\n掌握管理科学与工程学科的基础理论和系统的专业知识，培养敢于创新和善于思考的能力，了解本学科的最新研究成果，把握本学科的发展动态。本专业硕士毕业生\r\n应该熟练掌握管理科学与工程的基本理论和方法，能够有效地运用经济和管理理论，定性与定量相结合的分析方法及信息技术工具解决管理理论与实践中的问题；能\r\n够较熟练地掌握一门外国语，能够应用该外国语阅读本专业的文献资料。</span></p><p style=\"HEIGHT: auto; WHITE-SPACE: normal; WORD-SPACING: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-ALIGN: left; PADDING-TOP: 0px; FONT: 12px/21px 宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; ORPHANS: 2; WIDOWS: 2; LETTER-SPACING: normal; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span id=\"ContentBody\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 18px; HEIGHT: auto; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\">3</span><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 18px\">．身心健康，遵守纪律，有良好的道德品质。</span></p><p style=\"HEIGHT: auto; WHITE-SPACE: normal; WORD-SPACING: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-ALIGN: left; PADDING-TOP: 0px; FONT: 12px/21px 宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; ORPHANS: 2; WIDOWS: 2; LETTER-SPACING: normal; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 18px\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"HEIGHT: auto; WHITE-SPACE: normal; WORD-SPACING: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-ALIGN: left; PADDING-TOP: 0px; FONT: 12px/21px 宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; ORPHANS: 2; WIDOWS: 2; LETTER-SPACING: normal; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span id=\"ContentBody\" style=\"HEIGHT: auto; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\"><strong style=\"HEIGHT: auto; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 18px; HEIGHT: auto; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\">二、研究方向</span></strong></span></p><p style=\"HEIGHT: auto; WHITE-SPACE: normal; WORD-SPACING: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-ALIGN: left; PADDING-TOP: 0px; FONT: 12px/21px 宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; ORPHANS: 2; WIDOWS: 2; LETTER-SPACING: normal; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span id=\"ContentBody\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 18px; HEIGHT: auto; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\">1</span><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 18px\">．信息安全工程与信息系统</span></p><p style=\"HEIGHT: auto; WHITE-SPACE: normal; WORD-SPACING: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-ALIGN: left; PADDING-TOP: 0px; FONT: 12px/21px 宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; ORPHANS: 2; WIDOWS: 2; LETTER-SPACING: normal; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span id=\"ContentBody\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 18px; HEIGHT: auto; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\">2</span><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 18px\">．管理信息化与商务智能</span></p><p style=\"HEIGHT: auto; WHITE-SPACE: normal; WORD-SPACING: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-ALIGN: left; PADDING-TOP: 0px; FONT: 12px/21px 宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; ORPHANS: 2; WIDOWS: 2; LETTER-SPACING: normal; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span id=\"ContentBody\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 18px; HEIGHT: auto; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\">3</span><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 18px\">．电子商务与知识管理</span></p><p style=\"HEIGHT: auto; WHITE-SPACE: normal; WORD-SPACING: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-ALIGN: left; PADDING-TOP: 0px; FONT: 12px/21px 宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; ORPHANS: 2; WIDOWS: 2; LETTER-SPACING: normal; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 18px\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"HEIGHT: auto; WHITE-SPACE: normal; WORD-SPACING: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-ALIGN: left; PADDING-TOP: 0px; FONT: 12px/21px 宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; ORPHANS: 2; WIDOWS: 2; LETTER-SPACING: normal; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span id=\"ContentBody\" style=\"HEIGHT: auto; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\"><strong style=\"HEIGHT: auto; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 18px; HEIGHT: auto; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\">三、学习年限</span></strong></span></p><p style=\"HEIGHT: auto; WHITE-SPACE: normal; WORD-SPACING: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-ALIGN: left; PADDING-TOP: 0px; FONT: 12px/21px 宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; ORPHANS: 2; WIDOWS: 2; LETTER-SPACING: normal; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span id=\"ContentBody\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 18px; HEIGHT: auto; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\">学习年限为三年，均为脱产学习。对于提前完成规定学业，成绩特别优秀的研究生，按照相关规定可以申请提前毕业，但学习时间不少于两年。</span></p><p style=\"HEIGHT: auto; WHITE-SPACE: normal; WORD-SPACING: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-ALIGN: left; PADDING-TOP: 0px; FONT: 12px/21px 宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; ORPHANS: 2; WIDOWS: 2; LETTER-SPACING: normal; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 18px\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"HEIGHT: auto; WHITE-SPACE: normal; WORD-SPACING: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-ALIGN: left; PADDING-TOP: 0px; FONT: 12px/21px 宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; ORPHANS: 2; WIDOWS: 2; LETTER-SPACING: normal; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span id=\"ContentBody\" style=\"HEIGHT: auto; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 18px; HEIGHT: auto; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\">四、</span><strong style=\"HEIGHT: auto; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 18px; HEIGHT: auto; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\">培养方式</span></strong></span></p><p style=\"HEIGHT: auto; WHITE-SPACE: normal; WORD-SPACING: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-ALIGN: left; PADDING-TOP: 0px; FONT: 12px/21px 宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; ORPHANS: 2; WIDOWS: 2; LETTER-SPACING: normal; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span id=\"ContentBody\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 18px; HEIGHT: auto; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\">采取导师负责与导师指导小组共同培养的方式。</span><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 18px\">研究生的学习采用系统的基础理论学习与科学研究相结合、导师指导与研究生自学相结合、理论与实践相结合的方法，注重科研能力与创新能力的培养，加强研究生的自学能力、动手能力、表达能力和写作能力的训练和培养。</span></p><p style=\"HEIGHT: auto; WHITE-SPACE: normal; WORD-SPACING: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-ALIGN: left; PADDING-TOP: 0px; FONT: 12px/21px 宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; ORPHANS: 2; WIDOWS: 2; LETTER-SPACING: normal; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span id=\"ContentBody\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 18px; HEIGHT: auto; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\">研究生在导师的指导下制定出个人培养计划，对课程学习、学术活动与文献阅读、专业实践、开题报告、学位论文等要求和进度做出计划和安排。</span></p><p style=\"HEIGHT: auto; WHITE-SPACE: normal; WORD-SPACING: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-ALIGN: left; PADDING-TOP: 0px; FONT: 12px/21px 宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; ORPHANS: 2; WIDOWS: 2; LETTER-SPACING: normal; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 18px\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"HEIGHT: auto; WHITE-SPACE: normal; WORD-SPACING: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-ALIGN: left; PADDING-TOP: 0px; FONT: 12px/21px 宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; ORPHANS: 2; WIDOWS: 2; LETTER-SPACING: normal; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span id=\"ContentBody\" style=\"HEIGHT: auto; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 18px; HEIGHT: auto; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\">五、</span><strong style=\"HEIGHT: auto; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 18px; HEIGHT: auto; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\">课程设置及要求</span></strong></span></p><p style=\"HEIGHT: auto; WHITE-SPACE: normal; WORD-SPACING: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-ALIGN: left; PADDING-TOP: 0px; FONT: 12px/21px 宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; ORPHANS: 2; WIDOWS: 2; LETTER-SPACING: normal; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span id=\"ContentBody\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 18px; HEIGHT: auto; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\">１．课程分为学位课、必修课、选修课三大类。学位课程经考试合格并达到70</span><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 18px\">分（含70分）以上，方可获得学分，其他课程按规定进行考试或考查，成绩60分即可获得学分。</span></p><p style=\"HEIGHT: auto; WHITE-SPACE: normal; WORD-SPACING: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-ALIGN: left; PADDING-TOP: 0px; FONT: 12px/21px 宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; ORPHANS: 2; WIDOWS: 2; LETTER-SPACING: normal; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span id=\"ContentBody\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 18px; HEIGHT: auto; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\">２．选修课程中，按教育部要求，</span><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 18px\">“自然辩证法概论”和“马克思主义与社会科学方法论”两门课程必须选择1门修读，18学时，1学分。其它选修课由学生与导师协商，并由导师最终负责确定。在导师指导下，研究生可在本学科所设选修课及其他学科开设的课程范围内选择。</span></p><p style=\"HEIGHT: auto; WHITE-SPACE: normal; WORD-SPACING: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-ALIGN: left; PADDING-TOP: 0px; FONT: 12px/21px 宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; ORPHANS: 2; WIDOWS: 2; LETTER-SPACING: normal; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span id=\"ContentBody\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 18px; HEIGHT: auto; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\">３．同等学力及跨专业报考的研究生应在导师指导下，于第一学年完成《管理学》、《西方经济学》、《数据结构》、《管理信息系统》4</span><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 18px\">门本科核心课程的学习。补修课程考试成绩60分为合格。补修课程的成绩不合格，不能取得论文答辩资格。</span></p><p style=\"HEIGHT: auto; WHITE-SPACE: normal; WORD-SPACING: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-ALIGN: left; PADDING-TOP: 0px; FONT: 12px/21px 宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; ORPHANS: 2; WIDOWS: 2; LETTER-SPACING: normal; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span id=\"ContentBody\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 18px; HEIGHT: auto; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\">研究生教学设置计划见附件一。</span></p><p style=\"HEIGHT: auto; WHITE-SPACE: normal; WORD-SPACING: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-ALIGN: left; PADDING-TOP: 0px; FONT: 12px/21px 宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; ORPHANS: 2; WIDOWS: 2; LETTER-SPACING: normal; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 18px\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"HEIGHT: auto; WHITE-SPACE: normal; WORD-SPACING: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-ALIGN: left; PADDING-TOP: 0px; FONT: 12px/21px 宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; ORPHANS: 2; WIDOWS: 2; LETTER-SPACING: normal; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span id=\"ContentBody\" style=\"HEIGHT: auto; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 18px; HEIGHT: auto; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\">六、</span><strong style=\"HEIGHT: auto; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 18px; HEIGHT: auto; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\">其它培养环节</span></strong></span></p><p style=\"HEIGHT: auto; WHITE-SPACE: normal; WORD-SPACING: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-ALIGN: left; PADDING-TOP: 0px; FONT: 12px/21px 宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; ORPHANS: 2; WIDOWS: 2; LETTER-SPACING: normal; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span id=\"ContentBody\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 18px; HEIGHT: auto; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\">除课程学习外，研究生需完成专业实践、学术活动与文献阅读等培养环节。</span></p><p style=\"HEIGHT: auto; WHITE-SPACE: normal; WORD-SPACING: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-ALIGN: left; PADDING-TOP: 0px; FONT: 12px/21px 宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; ORPHANS: 2; WIDOWS: 2; LETTER-SPACING: normal; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span id=\"ContentBody\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 18px; HEIGHT: auto; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\">专业实践要求学生参加教学实践或社会实践。实践须有明确的内容要求、合理的时间安排和相应的考核。硕士研究生在完成专业实践后应写出实践报告（3000</span><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 18px\">字左右），填写实习鉴定表并交导师评阅，合格者计1学分。</span></p><p style=\"HEIGHT: auto; WHITE-SPACE: normal; WORD-SPACING: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-ALIGN: left; PADDING-TOP: 0px; FONT: 12px/21px 宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; ORPHANS: 2; WIDOWS: 2; LETTER-SPACING: normal; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span id=\"ContentBody\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 18px; HEIGHT: auto; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\">为掌握学科发展的研究前沿、拓宽视野，硕士研究生在学期间须积极参加学术讲座、学术研讨会，或在导师组指导下按学科自行组织专题讨论会。</span><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 18px\">每位研究生在第五学期结束前参加校内、校外的学术活动不少于6次，总量完成后填入统一格式的学术报告册(至少一次校际学术交流)。</span></p><p style=\"HEIGHT: auto; WHITE-SPACE: normal; WORD-SPACING: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-ALIGN: left; PADDING-TOP: 0px; FONT: 12px/21px 宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; ORPHANS: 2; WIDOWS: 2; LETTER-SPACING: normal; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span id=\"ContentBody\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 18px; HEIGHT: auto; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\">研究生在校学习期间应根据本学科的研究方向，阅读一定数量的经典著作和中外文献资料，并写出读书报告交导师评阅。</span></p><p style=\"HEIGHT: auto; WHITE-SPACE: normal; WORD-SPACING: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-ALIGN: left; PADDING-TOP: 0px; FONT: 12px/21px 宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; ORPHANS: 2; WIDOWS: 2; LETTER-SPACING: normal; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span id=\"ContentBody\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 18px; HEIGHT: auto; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\">完成以上学术活动及文献阅读,</span><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 18px\">导师评价合格后计1学分。</span></p><p style=\"HEIGHT: auto; WHITE-SPACE: normal; WORD-SPACING: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-ALIGN: left; PADDING-TOP: 0px; FONT: 12px/21px 宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; ORPHANS: 2; WIDOWS: 2; LETTER-SPACING: normal; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 18px\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"HEIGHT: auto; WHITE-SPACE: normal; WORD-SPACING: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-ALIGN: left; PADDING-TOP: 0px; FONT: 12px/21px 宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; ORPHANS: 2; WIDOWS: 2; LETTER-SPACING: normal; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span id=\"ContentBody\" style=\"HEIGHT: auto; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 18px; HEIGHT: auto; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\">七、</span><strong style=\"HEIGHT: auto; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 18px; HEIGHT: auto; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\">考核</span></strong></span></p><p style=\"HEIGHT: auto; WHITE-SPACE: normal; WORD-SPACING: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-ALIGN: left; PADDING-TOP: 0px; FONT: 12px/21px 宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; ORPHANS: 2; WIDOWS: 2; LETTER-SPACING: normal; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span id=\"ContentBody\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 18px; HEIGHT: auto; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\">１．考核方式分为考试与考查两种。学位课、必修课须采用考试（笔试）方式。选修课程可以采用考试或考查（课程研究报告、读书笔记、论文等）方式，由任课教师决定。</span></p><p style=\"HEIGHT: auto; WHITE-SPACE: normal; WORD-SPACING: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-ALIGN: left; PADDING-TOP: 0px; FONT: 12px/21px 宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; ORPHANS: 2; WIDOWS: 2; LETTER-SPACING: normal; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span id=\"ContentBody\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 18px; HEIGHT: auto; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\">２．研究生在第四学期开题报告会前参加中期考核。中期考核具体工作按《广东商学院研究生中期考核办法》执行。</span></p><p style=\"HEIGHT: auto; WHITE-SPACE: normal; WORD-SPACING: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-ALIGN: left; PADDING-TOP: 0px; FONT: 12px/21px 宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; ORPHANS: 2; WIDOWS: 2; LETTER-SPACING: normal; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 18px\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"HEIGHT: auto; WHITE-SPACE: normal; WORD-SPACING: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-ALIGN: left; PADDING-TOP: 0px; FONT: 12px/21px 宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; ORPHANS: 2; WIDOWS: 2; LETTER-SPACING: normal; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span id=\"ContentBody\" style=\"HEIGHT: auto; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 18px; HEIGHT: auto; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\">八、</span><strong style=\"HEIGHT: auto; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 18px; HEIGHT: auto; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\">毕业学分及要求</span></strong></span></p><p style=\"HEIGHT: auto; WHITE-SPACE: normal; WORD-SPACING: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-ALIGN: left; PADDING-TOP: 0px; FONT: 12px/21px 宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; ORPHANS: 2; WIDOWS: 2; LETTER-SPACING: normal; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span id=\"ContentBody\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 18px; HEIGHT: auto; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\">研究生通过全部学位课程、必修课程，课程学分修满38</span><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 18px\">学分（含38学分）以上，且完成规定的专业实践、学术活动与文献阅读环节，公开发表1篇(含1篇)以上与本专业相关的学术论文，完成毕业（学位）论文并通过毕业（学位）论文答辩的，方可毕业。</span></p><p style=\"HEIGHT: auto; WHITE-SPACE: normal; WORD-SPACING: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-ALIGN: left; PADDING-TOP: 0px; FONT: 12px/21px 宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; ORPHANS: 2; WIDOWS: 2; LETTER-SPACING: normal; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span id=\"ContentBody\" style=\"HEIGHT: auto; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 18px; HEIGHT: auto; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\">九、</span><strong style=\"HEIGHT: auto; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 18px; HEIGHT: auto; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\">学位论文及学位授予</span></strong></span></p><p style=\"HEIGHT: auto; WHITE-SPACE: normal; WORD-SPACING: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-ALIGN: left; PADDING-TOP: 0px; FONT: 12px/21px 宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; ORPHANS: 2; WIDOWS: 2; LETTER-SPACING: normal; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span id=\"ContentBody\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 18px; HEIGHT: auto; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\">研究生通过全部学位课程且学位课程平均成绩不低于75</span><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 18px\">分（含75分），中期考核合格者，一般应在第四学期提交开题报告。研究生开题报告的主要内容包括：（1）选题的依据和目的；（2）选题的意义和价值；（3）国内外研究文献综述；（4）论文设计方案，实施计划进度及预测结果；（5）研究过程中可能遇到的问题及解决措施。</span></p><p style=\"HEIGHT: auto; WHITE-SPACE: normal; WORD-SPACING: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-ALIGN: left; PADDING-TOP: 0px; FONT: 12px/21px 宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; ORPHANS: 2; WIDOWS: 2; LETTER-SPACING: normal; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span id=\"ContentBody\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 18px; HEIGHT: auto; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\">学位论文的选题可由研究生选定后经导师审核认可，也可由导师指定。学位论文应当在研究内容或者研究方法或者研究视角等方面具有一定程度的创新性，格式规范，字数不少于3</span><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 18px\">万字。</span></p><p style=\"HEIGHT: auto; WHITE-SPACE: normal; WORD-SPACING: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-ALIGN: left; PADDING-TOP: 0px; FONT: 12px/21px 宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; ORPHANS: 2; WIDOWS: 2; LETTER-SPACING: normal; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span id=\"ContentBody\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 18px; HEIGHT: auto; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\">论文完成的进度是：第四学期确定论文选题，查阅资料，写出并通过开题报告；第五学期写出论文初稿，并向研究生指导小组就论文的进展情况提出中期报告；第六学期论文定稿。未经导师审阅通过的论文，不得提交答辩。</span></p><p style=\"HEIGHT: auto; WHITE-SPACE: normal; WORD-SPACING: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-ALIGN: left; PADDING-TOP: 0px; FONT: 12px/21px 宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; ORPHANS: 2; WIDOWS: 2; LETTER-SPACING: normal; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span id=\"ContentBody\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 18px; HEIGHT: auto; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\">研究生的学位论文应当按规定送校内外专家评阅，并由校内外专家组成答辩委员会进行答辩。具体要求按《广东商学院硕士学位论文工作规定》办理。</span></p><p style=\"HEIGHT: auto; WHITE-SPACE: normal; WORD-SPACING: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-ALIGN: left; PADDING-TOP: 0px; FONT: 12px/21px 宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; ORPHANS: 2; WIDOWS: 2; LETTER-SPACING: normal; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span id=\"ContentBody\" style=\"FONT-SIZE: 18px; HEIGHT: auto; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; PADDING-TOP: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px\">研究生通过全部学位课程、必修课程，课程学分修满38</span><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 18px\">学分（含38学分）以上，完成规定的专业实践、学术活动与文献阅读环节，公开发表1篇(含1篇)以上与本专业相关的学术论文，完成学位论文并通过学位论文答辩的，符合《广东商学院学位授予规定》者，方能获得本学科的硕士学位。</span></p><p style=\"HEIGHT: auto; WHITE-SPACE: normal; WORD-SPACING: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-ALIGN: left; PADDING-TOP: 0px; FONT: 12px/21px 宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; ORPHANS: 2; WIDOWS: 2; LETTER-SPACING: normal; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 18px\">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"HEIGHT: auto; WHITE-SPACE: normal; WORD-SPACING: 0px; TEXT-TRANSFORM: none; COLOR: rgb(51,51,51); PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; TEXT-ALIGN: left; PADDING-TOP: 0px; FONT: 12px/21px 宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; MARGIN: 0px; ORPHANS: 2; WIDOWS: 2; LETTER-SPACING: normal; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: rgb(255,255,255); TEXT-INDENT: 0px; -webkit-tex